data.description: Welcome to this 4bedroom 3.5 bathroom spacious two-story home designed with your comfort in mind. Featuring a beautifully remodeled open kitchen that flows seamlessly into the family room with luxury vinyl plank flooring.  This home offers 4 generous bedrooms in the established Jeffries Ranch Neighborhood.  Upstairs enjoy the large master bedroom and closet, and 3 additional bedrooms. Nestled on a generous lot, this property boasts an inviting pool, a beautifully landscaped backyard, and the added benefits of solar power and a solar battery.  Located near excellent schools, this charming neighborhood offers a mix of coastal charm, large lots, and tons of walking trails under beautiful, established trees. Near Guajome Park for walks with the dogs, and great playgrounds for the kids.   The expansive lot provides endless opportunities for outdoor enjoyment. Entertain friends and family by the pool, savor al fresco dining on the patio, or create your own garden paradise. Four Bedrooms: With four generously sized bedrooms, including a master suite with an en-suite bathroom, there's plenty of room for family and guests.  Don't miss your chance to call this 4-bedroom paradise home! Contact us today for a private tour and experience the charming and peaceful lifestyle you've been dreaming of!
